terminal-emulator (vendored)
============================

This module contains source code from the Termux project's terminal-emulator
library (https://github.com/termux/termux-app, tag v0.118.1, path
terminal-emulator/), which itself derives from jackpal/Android-Terminal-Emulator
(https://github.com/jackpal/Android-Terminal-Emulator).

Both upstream sources are licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.
See LICENSE in this directory for the full text. The Termux LICENSE.md at the
repo root explicitly carves out the terminal-emulator subdirectory as Apache
2.0, separate from the GPLv3 used by the rest of the Termux app.

YouCoded modifications to this module are limited to a single documented patch
(adding a `RawByteListener` interface to `TerminalEmulator.append`). All edits
are marked with `// YOUCODED PATCH` comments. See VENDORED.md for the patch
details, the vendoring procedure, and the re-vendor steps for future Termux
version bumps.

